---
title: Quick Pomegranate-Glazed Pork Steak with Israeli Couscous Salad & Garlic Yoghurt
description: Looking for a tasty midweek dinner option? This pomegranate-glazed pork is sure to pull through for you on hump day with
a burst of fruitiness to balance out a tender cut of pork. Make it extra nourishing with a bed of Israeli couscous to have you
galloping into the weekend.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
